Short:    GLQuake for AmigaOS4
Author:   glquake@libero.it (Max m3x Tretene)
Version:  1.09 - beta 3
Type:     game/shoot
Requires: AOS4.0 update3 + warp3d + ahi

This archive contains the full GLQuake source required to compile a
standard GLQuake running under AmigaOS4.0. 

GLQuake requires the developer archives from Warp3D and MiniGL and
compiles with gcc (clib2)

If you should encounter any problems, contact the author, 
Max Tretene: glquake@libero.it.

