Release note:

14 June 2005:
	- first public release (tested only on a microA1-mk2 / Radeon 7000 setup)
	- this version introduce multitexturing (on gfx cards which support it)
	- added a new -grabmouse switch to block the mouse inside the window (works
	  only with the -windowmode switch)	
	- there is no more need to increase the CLI stack
	- support skyboxes
	- if there isn't any sound card installed, run it with -nosound or you will get a GR	
	